A [[exchange|currency_exchange]] allowing trade between bitcoins and ILS (Israeli New Shekels).

Purchases of bitcoins and proceeds from redemptions are transferred through an Israeli bank.  Each trade incurs a 5 ILS fee.

##History
The exchange was announced on April 13th, 2011 (2.1). On June 30, 2011 the site closed down temporarily, and relaunched on August 1, 2011.

